data.text:
Here you’ll find a medical center that feels like family—a place where you don’t get lost in the shuffle. Where high quality, experienced professionals provide confidence and skilled, compassionate caregivers offer hope.

This kind of award-winning care has been our tradition since 1863. It continues today with a deep commitment to provide a lifeline for the health needs of the people of Hudson County by bringing together advanced medical technologies and state-of-the-art care:
